# ğŸ² Dicee Game

Dicee is a simple and interactive web-based dice game built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
The game simulates rolling two dice for **Player 1** and **Player 2**, and automatically declares the winner based on the randomly generated dice values.

This project is ideal for beginners who want to understand **DOM manipulation, event handling, and random number generation** in JavaScript.

